The,objective,of,spire,io,is,to,allow,developers,to,build,Web,and,mobile,applications,without,having,to,also,build,the,server,side,infrastructure,that,is,typically,needed,to,support,them,The,server,side,support,provided,by,spire,io,is,centered,upon,providing,infrastructure,for,developers,through,RESTful,API,s,and,scenario,specific,client,libraries,The,fundamental,building,blocks,of,spire,io,s,back,end,support,services,are,their,channel,and,subscription,resources,which,essentially,provide,the,backbone,for,communication,and,event,listeners,within,the,spire,io,infrastructure,Spire,io,currently,has,two,available,services,Messaging,which,provides,the,foundation,of,real,time,capabilities,to,applications,and,Identity,which,allows,developers,to,easily,integrate,user,registration,and,log,in,into,their,apps